#

Crispy Pork Schnitzel with Herb Potato Salad

35 min
$15
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

WheatEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free OptionDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

GermanAustrian

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodQuick Meal

Description

Golden, crispy pork schnitzel served with a refreshing herb potato salad for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • pork loin cutlets: 4 pieces
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2 large
  • breadcrumbs: 2 cups
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • vegetable oil: for frying
  • potatoes: 1 lb
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • fresh dill: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • white wine vinegar: 1 tbsp
  • garlic: 1 clove, minced
